\begin_layout Proof
方阵 
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{A}$
\end_inset

 有 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 个互异的实特征值，因此有 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 个独立的左、右特征向量。利用这些特征值、特征向量可以构造出三个方阵：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Matrix{\Lambda}:=\begin{bmatrix}\lambda_{1}\\
 & \ddots\\
 &  & \lambda_{n}
\end{bmatrix}\qquad\Matrix{L}:=\begin{bmatrix}\bra{L_{1}}\\
\vdots\\
\bra{L_{n}}
\end{bmatrix}\qquad\Matrix{R}:=\begin{bmatrix}\ket{R_{1}} & \cdots & \ket{R_{n}}\end{bmatrix}
\]

\end_inset

它们满足
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Matrix{L}\Matrix{A}=\Matrix{\Lambda}\Matrix{L}\qquad\Matrix{A}\Matrix{R}=\Matrix{R}\Matrix{\Lambda}
\]

\end_inset

根据引理 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "lem:orthogonal_eigenvectors"

\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{L}$
\end_inset

 与 
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{R}$
\end_inset

 都是可逆的，并且 
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{R}^{-1}$
\end_inset

 可以被用作 
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{L}$
\end_inset

：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Matrix{A}\Matrix{R}=\Matrix{R}\Matrix{\Lambda}\implies\Matrix{R}^{-1}\Matrix{A}=\Matrix{\Lambda}\Matrix{R}^{-1}\implies\Matrix{L}:=\Matrix{R}^{-1}\implies\Matrix{A}=\Matrix{L}^{-1}\Matrix{\Lambda}\Matrix{L}
\]

\end_inset

借助这个 
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{L}$
\end_inset

，可以定义 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 个「特征变量 (characteristic variables)」：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\ket{V(x,t)}=\begin{bmatrix}v_{1}(x,t)\\
\vdots\\
v_{n}(x,t)
\end{bmatrix}:=\begin{bmatrix}\ip{L_{1}}{U(x,t)}\\
\vdots\\
\ip{L_{n}}{U(x,t)}
\end{bmatrix}=\Matrix{L}\ket{U(x,t)}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{L}$
\end_inset

 与 
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{L}^{-1}$
\end_inset

 都是常数矩阵，因此可以与偏导数算符 
\begin_inset Formula $\partial_{t}$
\end_inset

 与 
\begin_inset Formula $\partial_{x}$
\end_inset

 交换顺序。于是，关于 
\begin_inset Formula $\ket{U}$
\end_inset

 的方程 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:multi_wave_system_linear"

\end_inset

 可以化为关于 
\begin_inset Formula $\ket{V}$
\end_inset

 的方程：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\left(\partial_{t}+\Matrix{A}\partial_{x}\right)\ket{U(x,t)} & =\big(\partial_{t}\underbrace{\Matrix{L}^{-1}\Matrix{L}}_{\Matrix{1}}+\underbrace{\Matrix{L}^{-1}\Matrix{\Lambda}\Matrix{L}}_{\Matrix{A}}\partial_{x}\big)\ket{U(x,t)}\\
 & =\Matrix{L}^{-1}\left(\partial_{t}+\Matrix{\Lambda}\partial_{x}\right)\underbrace{\Matrix{L}\ket{U(x,t)}}_{\ket{V(x,t)}}=\ket{0}
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset

即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\partial_{t}+\Matrix{\Lambda}\partial_{x}\right)\ket{V(x,t)}=\Matrix{L}\ket{0}=\ket{0}
\]

\end_inset

其中 
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{\Lambda}$
\end_inset

 是对角阵，因此这是 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 个独立的单波方程，称为「
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 重单波方程」：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\left(\partial_{t}+\lambda_{i}\partial_{x}\right)v_{i}(x,t)=0\qquad i=1,\dots,n\label{eq:multi_wave_decomposed}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

