\end_inset

 重单波方程（
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:multi_wave_decomposed"

\end_inset

 式）的过程中，用到了「
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{L}$
\end_inset

 及 
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{L}^{-1}$
\end_inset

 都是常数矩阵」的事实，它是「
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{A}$
\end_inset

 为常数矩阵」的推论。若将 
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{A}$
\end_inset

 放宽为「显式依赖于 
\begin_inset Formula $x,t$
\end_inset

 的方阵」：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\partial_{t}+\Matrix{A(x,t)}\partial_{x}\right)\ket{U(x,t)}=\ket{0}
\]

\end_inset

则 
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{A(x,t)}$
\end_inset

 的特征值 
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{\Lambda(x,t)}$
\end_inset

 需要逐点计算，方程的双曲性也要逐点分析。即使方程是处处双曲的，
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{L(x,t)}$
\end_inset

 及 
\begin_inset Formula $\Matrix{L(x,t)}^{-1}$
\end_inset

 也不再是常数矩阵，将它们与偏导数算符 
\begin_inset Formula $\partial_{t}$
\end_inset

 及 
\begin_inset Formula $\partial_{x}$
\end_inset

 交换顺序会产生（不含 
\begin_inset Formula $\partial_{t}\ket{U}$
\end_inset

 或 
\begin_inset Formula $\partial_{x}\ket{U}$
